findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions modifyLGEWhitelist(), createLGEWhitelist(), and getLGEWhitelistRound() use a loop to iterate through a list from the function argument. If there is a long list, the function will be aborted with an OUT_OF_GAS exception.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: Whitelister has excessive privileges to define what addresses are included/excluded from a whitelist round and initialize whitelist rounds.
